# Raw audio + heavy derived artifacts: hosted on the HF dataset repo
# (Ketose333/music-mood-recs-assets) instead of git — git LFS storage for
# these was ~7x over GitHub's free quota. app.py downloads them on demand via
# huggingface_hub (see _resolve() in app.py). Re-create locally with
# scripts/download_audio.py / scripts/extract_melspecs.py if needed.
/data/audio/
/data/jamendo/
/data/synth_audio/
/artifacts/melspecs/
/artifacts/embeddings.npy

